"{\"uid\": \"asbarez.com-international-olympic-committee-condemned-over-shameful-apology-to-azerbaijan\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremonies of the Paris Olympics on Aug. 11 At close of 2024 Olympics, Christian Solidarity International urges the IOC to \\\"live up to its own values\\\" Following the closing ceremony of the Paris Games, John Eibner, the president of Christian Solidarity International, on Sunday criticized the International Olympic Committee for \\\"providing political support for the perpetrators\\\" of the ethnic cleansing of Nagorno Karabakh.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 84, \"end\": 118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Solidarity_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christian Solidarity International\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Solidarity_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Solidarity_International\"}, {\"begin\": 129, \"end\": 132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.958312594268069e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Eibner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Eibner\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Eibner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Eibner\"}, {\"begin\": 246, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christian_Solidarity_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christian Solidarity International\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chri