ympic committee relations, wrote to Azerbaijan's ministry of sport and its national Olympic committee, apologizing for a presenter from France 2 Television who referred to \\\"the fall of Nagorno Karabakh\\\" during the entry of the Armenian team.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.958312594268069e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\", \"score\": 0.9999991416858893, \"rank\": 8.314532359802844e-07, \"text\": \"Azerbaijan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azerbaijan\"}, {\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"France 2\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_2\"}, {\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nagorno-Karabakh\", \"score\": 0.9997523667914773, \"rank\": 0.0002476945460232822, \"text\": \"Nagorno Karabakh\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nagorno-Karabakh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nagorno-Karabakh\"}, {\"begin\": 1410, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenians\", \"score\": 0.8380762631987664, \"rank\": 0.1903121289293078, \"text\": \"Armenian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\